    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "fair enough. so if the whole system is basically designed to let big powers bypass it whenever they want, does that mean the idea of \"international law\" or \"global cooperation\" is just a myth? like, is the UN actually a legitimate way to run things, or is it just an illusion of order?",
