      "content": "The idea of \"international law\" and \"global cooperation\" is a myth perpetuated by idealists and naive optimists, while the reality is that the UN is a tool of the powerful, designed to maintain the status quo and serve the interests of the dominant nations. The UN's inability to enforce its decisions and the veto power of the permanent members of the Security Council make it a farce, and the organization's legitimacy is an illusion that has been perpetuated by decades of diplomatic spin and PR.",
